text: Hi, doctor. I'm back from our last visit. Oh, I'm glad to see you again. I hope you're feeling better. How are you doing? I'm doing a lot better. I have no nausea and no stomachache anymore since the last time you helped me. Wow, that's really good to hear. So you can probably stop taking that medication I put you on since you're feeling a lot better. Sounds good, Doc. Thank you.
